         <div type="translation" ana="#b1" xml:id="tibe0001.translation" corresp="#tibe0001.transcription">
            <p>Aries Taurus [Gemi]ni [Cancer] Leo Virgo Libra [Scorpio Sagittarius] Capricorn Aquarius Pisces
                </p>
